      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it's been my pride and joy and I've babied it since day one. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
