    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously preserved performance coupe that defines the 'mint' standard. This specimen features a high-revving, twin-scroll turbocharged powerplant with flawless compression and zero oil consumption. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-fast dual-clutch transmission and an electronically controlled limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, with all bushings and dampers exhibiting original damping rates and no signs of fatigue. Braking is handled by multi-piston fixed calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing no thermal stress or grooving. Cosmetically, the finish retains its original factory luster with consistent micrometer readings across all panels. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
