    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition, looking and feeling exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are flawless without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of creasing, while the carpets and headliner are immaculate. Every button, dial, and digital display functions with crisp precision, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by factory-certified technicians. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to own a truly pristine, investment-grade example. Sold with a complete service history, all original manuals, and both sets of keys.",
